{"tid":604674,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲係咪開始要草錢plan結婚?","createTime":"2018-03-25T03:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T02:04:59.000Z","uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b87d7dadf115ca6f9f89fa6be13964b38ed26ca6","tid":604674,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"同男朋友拍左6年幾拖<br />\n呢個時勢講結婚乜都係錢，我地兩個都係搵得嗰15k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓又買唔起，租又唔夠錢，婚後又唔想同屋企人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n股票長揸都唔賺得幾多，有冇同路人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318eae9bd3201436e44f7366aea9d527ef14fb82","tid":604674,"uid":138197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:15:38.000Z","msg":"冇錢咪唔好結囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6c3ab2d439398e957a551056c3c5131c428c4c","tid":604674,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:17:41.000Z","msg":"窮人學人結婚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01a3506082b5cfc647be84b885961c710db8c28","tid":604674,"uid":95847,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:18:59.000Z","msg":"記著唔好生仔，正所謂，窮人生仔正仆街！"},{"pid":"af8455690603cfb3f38a30f4c0b9c9ad8c28c966","tid":604674,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:19:56.000Z","msg":"搬出黎住一年試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3070d2051d5fa270c9d593fd523011bdcd9017f1","tid":604674,"uid":138658,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"草你老母"},{"pid":"f6712d2ac05e526a935ed8c5aee4cfb5e7d334b2","tid":604674,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:24:57.000Z","msg":"咁咪撚結啦屌你老母想害死下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363e1e2d1daf426f93f110f888ab983996f6b311","tid":604674,"uid":66945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咪撚結啦屌你老母想害死下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個話結婚一定要生<br />\n冇諗過生，我自己好憎細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c86d0ef75d8899708392a0608dba4dc0fb3def","tid":604674,"uid":66945,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記著唔好生仔，正所謂，窮人生仔正仆街！</blockquote><br />\n我窮，我屋企唔窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係層樓應該會比呀哥結婚，父母喺外國住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793cc812f6393cbd585177d6ad0005938cc81680","tid":604674,"uid":27432,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"其實又唔好比港豬污染<br />\n咪兩個一齊儲錢結婚<br />\n住就無計啦，想再慳啲咪同屋企人住住先<br />\n唔想咪租新界樓平啲<br />\n睇你地兩個點諗姐"},{"pid":"ca728fb42c8c5650f40f687c7529692a1724d87d","tid":604674,"uid":146893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"其實結婚睇你地想點搞姐<br />\n<br />\n兩個人有共識，兩邊屋企人明白咁就好<br />\n邊D PART可以SKIP，邊D PART可以慳<br />\n如果屋企人肯嘅話<br />\n你地兩個注個冊，去個旅行，兩家人食個飯都搞掂啦<br />\n<br />\n如果係要好似童話，華禮般嘅婚禮個啲<br />\n真係無幾十萬都唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f88e036b626df69ba65d35527515e5386c44e90","tid":604674,"uid":66945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實結婚睇你地想點搞姐<br />\n<br />\n兩個人有共識，兩邊屋企人明白咁就好<br />\n邊D PART可以SKIP，邊D PART可以慳<br />\n如果屋企人肯嘅話<br />\n你地兩個注個冊，去個旅行，兩家人食個飯都搞掂啦<br />\n<br />\n如果係要好似童話，華禮般嘅婚禮個啲<br />\n真係無幾十萬都唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我真係想簡單注冊食飯就算<br />\n我唔鍾意大搞，好怕對住咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca3376fc6a9ae7e1bc8f7675fa47bad97e69d62","tid":604674,"uid":92017,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T04:35:27.000Z","msg":"草錢？定儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學下理財真係一生受用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n25歲真係差不多，最基本紀錄下每日各項支出，唔好咁大細，好似而家d人一儲到幾皮野就燒哂所有積蓄去歐洲旅行，返到黎又呻窮呻無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有訂下每個月一出糧要撥走幾多做儲蓄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2367eeff9d3cdb4f9a006a4c99c6a3dd55943dfd","tid":604674,"uid":29120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T04:37:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4552e377cc620418c58b2601c496fb430294136","tid":604674,"uid":135783,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"00c86d0ef75d8899708392a0608dba4dc0fb3def","tid":604674,"uid":66945,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記著唔好生仔，正所謂，窮人生仔正仆街！</blockquote><br />\n我窮，我屋企唔窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係層樓應該會比呀哥結婚，父母喺外國住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"得一層樓唔係窮 咁係咩？"},{"pid":"f8f2f53591f87981c0be274e4a0f8ee485475a9d","tid":604674,"uid":60651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4552e377cc620418c58b2601c496fb430294136","tid":604674,"uid":135783,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"00c86d0ef75d8899708392a0608dba4dc0fb3def","tid":604674,"uid":66945,"like":6,"disli